item.title: Basic
item.description: Use the core features of Privy for free. Enjoy our free features and continue growing your fandom.

item.title: Standard
item.description: Unlock many of our features that allow you to stand out from the rest. Features like upgrading your profile, priority support, and custom analytics to help you grow your fandom.

item.title: Premium
item.description: Get the VIP treatment with our Premium plan. Unlock all features and have a robust profile. Your profile will also be featured on our “Featured Creators” page. This plan is great for rising talents. Get seen by everyone.
